pl.polsl.matrixcalculatorweb
 
pl.polsl.matrixcalculatorweb.model
Covers two public interfaces IMatrix and IArithmetical, one own exception DimensionException and five public classes of model package presenting its implementation: Matrix, Calculator, Calculation, ElementDouble, ElementInteger.
pl.polsl.matrixcalculatorweb.resources
 
pl.polsl.matrixcalculatorweb.servlets
Covers five public servlet classes MainServlet, MatrixTablesServlet, ResultServlet, HistoryServlet, ErrorServlet containing the GUI of the program in form of html pages and controlling the flow of the program.
